news.title: Ahmedabad civic body seals 12 residential, 37 commercial units sans BU permission
news.para: The sealed houses are near Al Mubarak Residency in Danilimda. The civic body’s town planning and estate department also sealed 37 commercial units in areas such as Kubernagar, Odhav and Shahpur.

news.title: CREDAI plans to pump in Rs 10,000 crore during Rajasthan summit-2022
news.para: Along with this, three industrial cities will be developed in Jaipur city, in which about 2,000 industries will be established. Two integrated townships will also be developed, which will have about 3,000 plots.

news.title: L&T Metro Rail Hyderabad raises Rs 13,119 crore
news.para: ET reported on December 22 that the company was raising up to Rs 13,600 crore including Rs 8,600 crore worth of bonds and CPs of up to Rs 5,000 crore.
